# act configuration — runs automatically for every `act` invocation
#
# Runner image: catthehacker/ubuntu:act-22.04
#   - ~500 MB; has Python 3.x, Node.js, npm, git pre-installed
#   - Does NOT auto-pull on every run (--no-pull keeps pushes fast)
#   - First run: `act --pull` once to cache the image
#
# To pull the image manually the first time:
#   act push -W .github/workflows/ci.yml --pull
#
-P ubuntu-latest=catthehacker/ubuntu:act-22.04
--pull=false
--bind
